Blue River is offering London-based Mura CMS training April 28 - May 02, 2014. Sign up now and take advantage of the opportunity to learn Mura CMS directly from the expert team at Blue River.

These full-day training courses will provide you with in-depth understanding of how to get the most out of Mura CMS, from simple content updates all the way to creating new Mura CMS plug-ins. We have 3 courses available, each tailored to the unique needs of your different team members.

We'll be presenting this training in London at the fantastic etc.Venues location in Farringdon, London Burrough of Islington. The day will include a hot lunch, coffee and snacks, and of course a lot of Mura CMS!

For more information, please visit http://www.getmura.com/training/hosted-training/eu-training-courses/
